Date: Wed, 4 Sep 2019 11:19:32 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: sun8i-h3-nanopi: Add new board ZeroPi

Signed-off-by: The Going <48602507+The-going@users.noreply.github.com>
---
